title: 12 OCLOCK HIGH 214-215 [retr?tv]
description:
12 O&#039;CLOCK HIGH 

2x14. Between the Lines   12/13/1965 
The Invasion of Europe is coming and Stace & Krasker are flying back with information about Russian troop strength when their plane is shot down, one general jumps, the other rides the plane down with Trask who is afraid to jump.
  Guest star: Donald Harron (Master Sergeant Trask), Philip Bruns (Lieutenant Gargas), Larry Gates (Major General Stace), Ken Drake (Brigadier General Krasker), Sasha Harden (German Captain)

2x15. Target 802    12/27/1965 
On the way back from a bombing run over the Ruhr valley, bombs are accidentally dropped on Ste Monique. 1st Lieutenant Parks. the bombardier is interrogated. A single bomb fell in the village square killing resistance leaders Pierre Fecamp. Two pilots hiding in St Monique escaped, Major Coefield from the 918th and Captain Pollard from the 511th Fighter Squadron. Pollard has fallen in love with Claudine, the woman who rescued them. She has brought her son to England, he is badly wounded and may lose his leg. Claudine hates Gallagher and iplans to kill him.
  Guest star: Jean-Michel Michenaud (Jean-Paul Corbelle), Lisa Pera (Claudine Corbelle), Lou Antonio (Captain Pollard), Harry Townes (Brigadier General Marten), Anthony Zerbe (Captain Burgdorf), Jacques Roux (Marcel Lenoir), Wright King (Major Coefield)

XviD/640x480/47min
